<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ع ف ف:</span> <span class="c2">(عَفَّ)</span> عَنِ الْحَرَامِ يَعِفُّ بِالْكَسْرِ <span class="c2">(عِفَّةٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(عَفًّا)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(عَفَافَةً)</span> أَيْ كَفَّ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(عَفٌّ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(عَفِيفٌ)</span> وَالْمَرْأَةُ <span class="c2">(عَفَّةٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(عَفِيفَةٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَعَفَّهُ)</span> اللَّهُ. وَ <span class="c2">(اسْتَعَفَّ)</span> عَنِ الْمَسْأَلَةِ أَيْ عَفَّ. وَ <span class="c2">(تَعَفَّفَ)</span> تَكَلَّفَ <span class="c2">(الْعِفَّةَ)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>